        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324610" xml:id="d1e157954" corresp="Gautier II, évêque d'Autun 1189 -1223)">Gauterius, Dei gratia
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e157956" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Eduensis</placeName>
                        episcopus</persName>, notum facio presentibus et futuris quod <persName key="d1e25596" xml:id="d1e157960">Oliverius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e157962" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Grinione</placeName>
                    </persName> laudavit et concessit Deo et fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e157965" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">
                        <app>
                            <lem>Fonteneti</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">Fontenetensis</rdg>
                        </app>
                    </orgName>ecclesie omnes elemosinas quas pater suus et fratres sui eidem
                    ecclesie fecerant, simul et terram que dicitur <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324957" xml:id="d1e157972" corresp="Mons Arlaut">
                        <foreign>Mont Arlant</foreign>
                    </placeName> in bosco et plano. <app>
                        <lem>
                            <witEnd wit="#D" />
                            <witDetail wit="#D">Suite omise et résumée par trois extraits : Haec
                                omnia laudavit Floria uxor Oliverii, cum duobus filiis suis Pontio
                                et Hugone etc. Inter testes : Josbertus abbas Fontenetensis, anno ab
                                incarnatione Domini M. C. XCI.</witDetail>
                        </lem>
                    </app> Ita tamen quod fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e157983" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> et homines <persName key="d1e25602" xml:id="d1e157986">Oliverii</persName> boscum non exartabunt, terras autem planas fratres
                        <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e157989" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> sine
                    ulla custuma arare et excolere. Porro quicumque predictam terram excolere
                    voluerit fratribus de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e157992" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> tercias reddet, preter homines <persName key="d1e25608" xml:id="d1e157995">Oliverii</persName> quantum ad ipsius attinet porcionem.
                    Et quia discordia erat inter <persName key="d1e25614" xml:id="d1e157998">Oliverium</persName> et fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158002" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> de vadis concordatum est quod idem
                    fratres solitum vadum suum ita aptabunt et component ut per illud sine periculo
                    transire possint. Si vero vadum aliquo casu ita dirutum fuerit ut per ilud
                    transire non possint, per alia vada ubi poterunt libere et quiete transibut
                    donec vadum suum emendare possint. Per prata libere et quiete predicti fratres
                    carricabunt omni calumpnia et actione remota, excepto quod si per segetes aut
                    prata non secata aliquod dampnum fecerint. Ipsum dampnum quantum legitime
                    appreciatum fuerit sine alia emendatione restituent, pasturas et omnes aasentias
                    animalibus et pastoribus necessarias per totam terram suam ubicumque sit quas
                    predicti fratres in vadio habebant pro quingentis solidis <persName key="d1e25620" xml:id="d1e158005">Oliverius</persName> fratribus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158008" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> sine aliqua
                    retentione in elemosinam bona fide dedit et concessit. Propter quod ei jam dicte
                    summam pecunie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158011" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName> remiserunt. Preterea concessit <persName key="d1e25627" xml:id="d1e158014">Oliverius</persName> quod si <persName key="d1e25633" xml:id="d1e158017">dominus Osbertus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325304" xml:id="d1e158019" corresp="Joux">
                            <foreign>Joux</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName> in terra sua que de chasamento <persName key="d1e25639" xml:id="d1e158024">Oliverii</persName> est ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158027" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> elemosinam
                    facere voluerit usque ad <num>xii</num> carratas feni quales conversi facere
                    solent libere accipiant <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158033" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName>. Pro hiis omnibus <persName key="d1e25645" xml:id="d1e158036">Oliverius</persName> de beneficio ecclesie excepta
                    predicta pecunia <num>ccc</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">tos</hi> solidos habuit. Hujus rei testes sunt <persName key="d1e25651" xml:id="d1e158045">Josbertus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158047" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    </persName> et cum eo <num>iii</num> monachi <persName key="d1e25657" xml:id="d1e158053">Philippus</persName>, <persName key="d1e25664" xml:id="d1e158056">Bernardus</persName> et <persName key="d1e25670" xml:id="d1e158059">Humbertus</persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e158063" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo archipresbiter <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e158065" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25676" xml:id="d1e158068">Races capellanus de
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324470" xml:id="d1e158070" corresp="Lucenay-le-Duc (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Lucennaco</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25682" xml:id="d1e158073">Eniaubus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324991" xml:id="d1e158078" corresp="Puteolis">Puteolis</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25688" xml:id="d1e158084">Renerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#323218" xml:id="d1e158086" corresp="Frôlois (Côte-d'Or, Venarey,Montbard)">Frollesio</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25694" xml:id="d1e158089">Milo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324467" xml:id="d1e158091" corresp="Lantilly (Côte-d'Or, Semur-en-Auxois)">
                            <foreign>Lantille</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25701" xml:id="d1e158095">Renerius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324359" xml:id="d1e158097" corresp="Sainte-Colombe-en-Auxois (Côte-d'Or, Semur-en-Auxois)">Sancta Columba</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25707" xml:id="d1e158101">Willermus
                            <addName>Huldrei</addName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25713" xml:id="d1e158106">Willermus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e158108" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Curte Rabodi</placeName>
                    </persName>. Hec omnia laudavit <persName key="d1e25719" xml:id="d1e158111">Floria uxor <persName key="d1e25725" xml:id="d1e158113">Oliverii</persName>
                    </persName> cum duobus filiis suis <persName key="d1e25731" xml:id="d1e158116">Pontio</persName> et <persName key="d1e25738" xml:id="d1e158119">Hugone</persName>. Unde testes sunt <persName key="d1e25744" xml:id="d1e158122">Bernardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e158124" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Grinun</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25750" xml:id="d1e158129">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324349" xml:id="d1e158131" corresp="Quincy-le-Vicomte (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Quinci</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <hi rend="background(green)">monachi Fonteneti</hi>, et duo
                    conversi frater <persName key="d1e25756" xml:id="d1e158138">Rainadus magister
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324451" xml:id="d1e158140" corresp="Flacey (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Flaceii</placeName>
                    </persName> et frater <persName key="d1e25762" xml:id="d1e158143">Waldricus</persName> ; <persName key="d1e25768" xml:id="d1e158146">Willermus <addName>
                            <foreign>Uldrez</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e25775" xml:id="d1e158152">Petrus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325039" xml:id="d1e158154" corresp="Valle">Valle</placeName>
                    </persName>. Postea querelam movit <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158158" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensibus</orgName>
                    <persName key="d1e25781" xml:id="d1e158160">Oliverius</persName> de prato quod
                    ab homine suo emerant et de quodam fossato quod ante <sic corresp="#C">molidinum</sic> suum fecerant propter quod molendinum suum plurimum
                    deterioratum fuisse et se urgens dampnum inde recepisse dicebat et terra sua
                    quam eo nesciente ad <term>lavam trahendam ruperant et excavaverant</term>. De
                    hiis <persName key="d1e25787" xml:id="d1e158169">abbas Fonteneti</persName> et
                        <persName key="d1e25793" xml:id="d1e158172">Oliverius</persName> posuerunt
                    se super hos <num>iiii</num>
                    <hi rend="superscript">or</hi>, scilicet <persName key="d1e25799" xml:id="d1e158181">Pontium de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#323218" xml:id="d1e158183" corresp="Frôlois (Côte-d'Or, Venarey,Montbard)">Frollesio</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e158186" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odonem
                        archipresbiterum</persName>, <persName key="d1e25805" xml:id="d1e158189">Philippum de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e158191" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Curte
                            Rabodi</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25812" xml:id="d1e158194">Teobaudum prepositum
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e158196" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Montis
                            Barri</placeName>
                    </persName>, qui concorditer dixerunt quod <persName key="d1e25818" xml:id="d1e158200">Oliverius</persName> de prefato molendino justam
                    querimoniam non haberet. Pro aliis vero querelis omnibus pacificandis dixerunt
                    predicti dictores quos <persName key="d1e25824" xml:id="d1e158203">abbas
                        Fonteneti</persName> de beneficio ecclesie carta ista sigillata <persName key="d1e25830" xml:id="d1e158206">Oliverio</persName>
                    <num>x</num> libras daret. Hinc testes sunt <persName key="d1e25836" xml:id="d1e158211">Josbertus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e158213" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25842" xml:id="d1e158216">Philippus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e158218" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Curte Robodi</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25849" xml:id="d1e158222">Bernardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e158224" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Grinun</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25855" xml:id="d1e158228">Johannes <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e158230" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Montis Barri</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e158233" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo
                        archipresbiter</persName>, <persName key="d1e25861" xml:id="d1e158236">Poncius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#323218" xml:id="d1e158238" corresp="Frôlois (Côte-d'Or, Venarey,Montbard)">Frollesio</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25867" xml:id="d1e158241">Odo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e158243" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Marmania</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25873" xml:id="d1e158246">Teobaudus prepositus
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e158248" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Montis
                            Barri</placeName>
                    </persName>, <persName key="d1e25879" xml:id="d1e158252">Petrus avunculus
                        ejus</persName>, <persName key="d1e25886" xml:id="d1e158255">Milo <addName>
                            <foreign>Corbille</foreign>
                        </addName>
                    </persName>. Nos quoque ad testimonium horum atque munimen presenti carte
                    sigillum nostrum apponimus et hiis scienter obviantes anathemate condampnamus,
                    anno ab incarnatione Domini <num>m° c° xc° i°</num>.</p>
